# ── PROJECT LAYER — this IS a project fork, not the seed ────────────────────
# storage/ and src/components/specialized/ ARE tracked in project repos.
# They are only excluded in the seed (Agnostic_System_Seed).
# When pulling upstream/main from the seed, these paths are never touched
# because the seed never has files there.

